  08 Dec 2005; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org> vdr-1.3.27.ebuild,
  vdr-1.3.34.ebuild, vdr-1.3.34-r1.ebuild, vdr-1.3.34-r2.ebuild,
